(json 9 (id 38))
(json 9 (name "RFP Design"))
(json 9 (slug "rfp-design"))
(json 9 (max_funding_amount "25000"))
(json 9 (description "Select this Pool if you have a great idea and want to get funded for making detailed specifications (RFPs - Requests For Proposal) that will allow any development team to submit a realistic proposal.

Deep Funding is developing a new proposal creation and selection process based on 'Request For Proposals' (RFPs). This inlcudes the option to get rewarded for making RFPs; high quality specifications for projects that are desired by our community. 



This pool enables the community to select a MAX of *3* proposals. Awarded teams will get funded for the creation of an RFP according to the template provided by DF. 


After completion, the DF team will allocate a Max budget and the RFP will be published on the DF website and opened for proposals from development teams. "))
